"'''Secrets of Mos Eisley'''" was a [[Star Wars Roleplaying Game]] source article published in [[Star Wars Gamer 7|''Star Wars Gamer'' 7]]. It was written by [[Peter M. Schweighofer]] and illustrated by [[Derek Thompson]].

